TweetsFS

TweetsFS is Web application project to save and share your Favorite Twitter Tweets.
Project Salient features:

Project uses the twitter API and Twitter4J Library.

* Save (Persist) Favorite Tweets of the User to REDIS NoSQL Data Store
* Show all the Tweets marked Favorite by a User
  * Filter By User
  * Filter By Time (Chronological)
* Resolve and fetch the HTML / Pages embedded in tweets via bit.ly, t.co etc.
* Share the saved tweets via HTML EMail
